*SAMPA: /"jU@r@U/

=== Noun ===
'''euro''' (''plural'' '''euros''' or '''euro''' if refering to currency)

#The currency of the [[European Monetary Union]], sometimes [[Euro]]
#Prefix used to denote something being of or from [[Europe]] (e.g. [[Eurozone]], [[eurotrash]])

