===Plurals===
It is worth noting that the official plural for the currency is '''euro''' in all [[EU]] official languages, however, most parts of the [[Eurozone]] use their own plural, except for English, as, in Ireland (the only English speaking euro member) ''euro'' is also used as the plural.
